1
00:03:06,120 --> 00:03:07,720
You've been traveling alone

2
00:03:08,560 --> 00:03:10,320
and must be exhausted.

3
00:03:12,000 --> 00:03:13,040
Today,

4
00:03:14,720 --> 00:03:16,560
with the rustic charm

5
00:03:17,760 --> 00:03:20,020
and beautiful scenery of the mountains,

6
00:03:20,200 --> 00:03:21,079
why don't you

7
00:03:24,640 --> 00:03:25,880
spend it with me?

8
00:03:48,320 --> 00:03:49,180
Unbelievable.

9
00:03:50,880 --> 00:03:53,880
I dressed up like this and still couldn't win you over.

10
00:03:54,360 --> 00:03:55,160
Just you wait.

11
00:04:46,240 --> 00:04:47,840
How can you sleep so soundly?

12
00:04:48,680 --> 00:04:49,210
Let's go.

13
00:04:59,200 --> 00:05:00,080
Hurry up.

14
00:06:13,280 --> 00:06:14,200
Master.

15
00:06:16,920 --> 00:06:17,920
It seems

16
00:06:18,040 --> 00:06:19,720
another extraordinary person

17
00:06:19,720 --> 00:06:21,200
has arrived in the city.

18
00:06:39,920 --> 00:06:41,080
Want to buy a talisman?

19
00:06:41,080 --> 00:06:42,080
Good luck charms.

20
00:06:42,200 --> 00:06:43,130
Wealth pouches.

21
00:06:43,600 --> 00:06:44,460
Peace amulets.

22
00:06:44,840 --> 00:06:46,240
Things to pray for peace,

23
00:06:46,840 --> 00:06:47,640
we have it all.

24
00:06:48,320 --> 00:06:50,040
No, thanks. I already have one.

25
00:06:50,040 --> 00:06:50,640
Thank you.

26
00:06:53,680 --> 00:06:54,080
Want to buy a talisman?

27
00:06:54,080 --> 00:06:54,600
No, thanks.

28
00:06:54,600 --> 00:06:55,280
I really don't need it.

29
00:06:55,280 --> 00:06:55,920
I have one.

30
00:06:57,000 --> 00:06:58,260
Want to buy a talisman?

31
00:06:58,920 --> 00:06:59,920
Good luck charms.

32
00:07:00,800 --> 00:07:01,730
Wealth pouches.

33
00:07:02,680 --> 00:07:03,540
Peace amulets.

34
00:07:04,600 --> 00:07:04,920
No, thanks.

35
00:07:04,920 --> 00:07:06,320
Things to pray for peace,

36
00:07:06,920 --> 00:07:07,720
we have it all.

37
00:07:09,080 --> 00:07:10,240
Want to buy a talisman?

38
00:07:10,240 --> 00:07:11,240
Good luck charms.

39
00:07:11,440 --> 00:07:12,370
Wealth pouches.

40
00:07:12,760 --> 00:07:14,000
Want to buy a talisman?

41
00:07:14,000 --> 00:07:15,000
Good luck charms.

42
00:07:15,120 --> 00:07:16,050
Wealth pouches.

43
00:07:16,280 --> 00:07:17,140
Peace amulets.

44
00:07:25,600 --> 00:07:26,080
Master.

45
00:07:26,600 --> 00:07:27,860
What are we doing here?

46
00:07:28,120 --> 00:07:29,440
Let's stay here first.

47
00:07:30,400 --> 00:07:31,080
Stay here?

48
00:07:31,440 --> 00:07:32,970
It will cost a lot of silver.

49
00:07:34,320 --> 00:07:35,580
Don't you have silver?

50
00:07:35,920 --> 00:07:38,720
This silver is to be handed over to the government.

51
00:07:38,920 --> 00:07:39,760
Handing it over

52
00:07:39,760 --> 00:07:41,020
is official business.

53
00:07:41,200 --> 00:07:42,520
Since it's official business,

54
00:07:42,520 --> 00:07:44,120
we must do things by the book.

55
00:07:44,920 --> 00:07:46,850
We can't just sleep on the streets.

56
00:08:17,680 --> 00:08:18,760
Are you two

57
00:08:19,160 --> 00:08:20,040
staying

58
00:08:20,320 --> 00:08:21,440
or bathing?

59
00:08:23,320 --> 00:08:23,920
We'll stay

60
00:08:24,800 --> 00:08:25,440
and bathe.

61
00:08:26,840 --> 00:08:28,400
You really have a good eye.

62
00:08:28,880 --> 00:08:29,680
Ercheng

63
00:08:29,840 --> 00:08:31,400
is famous for its hot springs.

64
00:08:31,400 --> 00:08:32,600
And Miaoren Bathhouse

65
00:08:32,600 --> 00:08:34,080
is the best in Ercheng.

66
00:08:34,799 --> 00:08:35,679
Coming here,

67
00:08:36,240 --> 00:08:38,100
you'll definitely be satisfied.

68
00:08:38,840 --> 00:08:39,200
Then

69
00:08:39,720 --> 00:08:41,320
we'll book two deluxe rooms.

70
00:08:41,799 --> 00:08:43,260
One deluxe room is enough.

71
00:08:51,720 --> 00:08:53,160
I spoke too much.

72
00:08:54,080 --> 00:08:55,210
Please go upstairs.

73
00:08:55,960 --> 00:08:56,280
Xiao Wang.

74
00:08:56,280 --> 00:08:56,880
Xiao Wang.

75
00:08:57,440 --> 00:08:57,900
Coming.

76
00:08:58,080 --> 00:08:59,680
Please go upstairs, you two.

77
00:09:08,440 --> 00:09:09,240
Miss,

78
00:09:09,640 --> 00:09:10,640
do you want to stay

79
00:09:11,040 --> 00:09:12,370
or enjoy the hot spring?

80
00:09:25,720 --> 00:09:26,320
Master.

81
00:09:26,720 --> 00:09:27,920
Since it's on public expense,

82
00:09:27,920 --> 00:09:29,380
why don't we get two rooms?

83
00:09:29,480 --> 00:09:30,680
There's only one bed.

84
00:09:31,120 --> 00:09:32,440
We should spend what we need to spend,

85
00:09:32,440 --> 00:09:33,170
and save what

86
00:09:33,520 --> 00:09:34,180
we can save.

87
00:09:35,920 --> 00:09:37,520
So everything goes by your rules.

88
00:09:37,520 --> 00:09:38,650
What are you saying?

89
00:09:39,160 --> 00:09:39,690
Nothing.

90
00:09:40,480 --> 00:09:41,320
You sleep on the bed.

91
00:09:41,320 --> 00:09:42,650
I'll sleep on the floor.

92
00:09:44,880 --> 00:09:45,920
The hot spring here

93
00:09:45,920 --> 00:09:46,980
seems to be famous.

94
00:09:47,480 --> 00:09:48,880
You are tired from the journey.

95
00:09:48,880 --> 00:09:50,810
Why not take a dip in the hot spring?

96
00:09:50,920 --> 00:09:52,520
It can relieve your fatigue.

97
00:09:52,520 --> 00:09:52,920
Okay.

98
00:09:53,320 --> 00:09:55,380
I haven't been in a hot spring before.

99
00:10:01,880 --> 00:10:02,340
Master,

100
00:10:02,760 --> 00:10:03,760
aren't you going?

101
00:10:03,920 --> 00:10:05,520
I want to be alone for a while.

102
00:10:05,680 --> 00:10:07,320
After you finish with the hot spring,

103
00:10:07,320 --> 00:10:09,320
remember to ask for a set of bedding.

104
00:10:09,800 --> 00:10:10,280
Okay.

105
00:10:13,960 --> 00:10:15,280
Still shy.

106
00:10:45,920 --> 00:10:46,560
Master.

107
00:10:48,080 --> 00:10:50,610
Those three checked into Miaoren Hot Spring.

108
00:10:51,040 --> 00:10:51,920
One of them

109
00:10:52,480 --> 00:10:53,520
is taking a bath.

110
00:10:54,880 --> 00:10:55,920
The other two

111
00:10:56,320 --> 00:10:58,320
are resting in their own rooms.

112
00:10:58,880 --> 00:11:01,080
The three of them are all separated.

113
00:11:02,640 --> 00:11:04,920
Seems they don't have much capability.

114
00:11:08,600 --> 00:11:09,280
Go.

115
00:11:09,960 --> 00:11:11,040
Go meet them.

116
00:11:11,240 --> 00:11:12,440
If they are obedient,

117
00:11:12,800 --> 00:11:14,360
keep them penned up.

118
00:11:14,880 --> 00:11:16,520
If they are not,

119
00:11:17,920 --> 00:11:20,400
just feed them to the little ones.

120
00:11:43,520 --> 00:11:44,450
So comfortable.

121
00:11:45,120 --> 00:11:47,040
Why not enjoy it since we paid for it?

122
00:11:47,040 --> 00:11:49,770
This master is indeed different from us mortals.

123
00:11:51,720 --> 00:11:53,760
Truly different.

124
00:12:01,080 --> 00:12:02,400
It feels so good.

125
00:12:05,360 --> 00:12:06,120
Not bad.

126
00:12:07,280 --> 00:12:08,080
Young master.

127
00:12:09,320 --> 00:12:11,050
Don't be afraid, young master.

128
00:12:11,080 --> 00:12:12,400
It's me.

129
00:12:13,320 --> 00:12:14,000
Madam.

130
00:12:14,640 --> 00:12:16,640
We paid silver to bathe in this hot spring.

131
00:12:16,640 --> 00:12:18,500
You must be joking, young master.

132
00:12:18,920 --> 00:12:20,280
I just came to ask

133
00:12:20,920 --> 00:12:22,120
if you are satisfied

134
00:12:22,640 --> 00:12:23,800
with our hot spring.

135
00:12:24,520 --> 00:12:25,380
The hot spring?

136
00:12:25,640 --> 00:12:26,560
It's excellent.

137
00:12:26,560 --> 00:12:27,220
Excellent.

138
00:12:39,480 --> 00:12:41,080
Please enjoy, young master.

139
00:12:46,080 --> 00:12:46,480
Is this

140
00:12:47,280 --> 00:12:47,880
free?

141
00:12:50,440 --> 00:12:52,520
You are really joking, young master.

142
00:12:52,800 --> 00:12:54,860
This is complimentary from the shop.

143
00:12:54,920 --> 00:12:56,600
There's more if it's not enough.

144
00:12:56,600 --> 00:12:57,720
I'll give you

145
00:12:58,720 --> 00:12:59,920
as much as you want.

146
00:13:01,080 --> 00:13:02,760
Then I won't be polite.

147
00:13:10,920 --> 00:13:12,520
Eat slowly, young master.

148
00:13:14,880 --> 00:13:16,320
Are there any more grapes?

149
00:13:16,320 --> 00:13:17,250
Bring some more.

150
00:13:20,080 --> 00:13:20,560
Okay.

151
00:13:21,720 --> 00:13:23,050
Once you finish eating,

152
00:13:23,440 --> 00:13:24,560
I will go get them.

153
00:13:36,000 --> 00:13:37,720
Where are you from?

154
00:13:38,520 --> 00:13:40,120
What are you doing in Er City?

155
00:13:40,480 --> 00:13:42,320
We're looking for the local authorities.

156
00:13:42,320 --> 00:13:43,920
Why are you looking for them?

157
00:13:44,520 --> 00:13:46,320
Looking for the authorities...

158
00:13:49,480 --> 00:13:50,200
My master

159
00:13:50,720 --> 00:13:51,520
told me not to speak carelessly.

160
00:13:51,520 --> 00:13:52,240
Master?

161
00:13:54,240 --> 00:13:55,320
What master?

162
00:13:56,720 --> 00:13:58,380
The master staying upstairs.

163
00:13:58,640 --> 00:14:00,480
He's an amazing demon hunter.

164
00:14:07,400 --> 00:14:09,000
Sorry.

165
00:14:15,080 --> 00:14:15,880
It's okay.

166
00:14:17,200 --> 00:14:19,080
The master you just mentioned,

167
00:14:19,840 --> 00:14:20,800
is he Taoist

168
00:14:21,080 --> 00:14:22,000
or Buddhist?

169
00:14:23,240 --> 00:14:23,720
Well,

170
00:14:24,280 --> 00:14:25,410
I don't know either.

171
00:14:25,440 --> 00:14:27,040
Anyway, he's just really powerful.

172
00:14:27,040 --> 00:14:28,970
Then you must be very powerful too.

173
00:14:29,240 --> 00:14:29,800
Me?

174
00:14:30,560 --> 00:14:32,020
I'm not very powerful yet.

175
00:14:32,320 --> 00:14:32,720
But

176
00:14:33,440 --> 00:14:35,100
I want to become his disciple.

177
00:14:35,200 --> 00:14:35,880
Given time,

178
00:14:36,840 --> 00:14:39,300
I will definitely become very powerful too.

179
00:14:47,560 --> 00:14:48,400
So,

180
00:14:49,000 --> 00:14:50,400
he is just an easy target.

181
00:14:51,320 --> 00:14:52,720
Let's kill him first,

182
00:14:53,280 --> 00:14:54,680
then deal with those two.

183
00:16:02,160 --> 00:16:03,160
Ping Jieqiang Hai Hui.
